abstract: The Justice Department asked a small Northern California-based Internet provider to cough up information about one of its customers, a self-described WikiLeaks supporter. It fought back.
snippet: The Justice Department asked a small Northern California-based Internet provider to cough up information about one of its customers, a self-described WikiLeaks supporter. It fought back.
lead_paragraph: The Obama administration has found an unlikely adversary in wine country.

headline.main: Wine Country Internet Provider Takes On Justice Department
